Packages
suncertify.app Provides classes for the main application (server, local and remote clients) of the Customer Service Representative (CSR) Graphical User Interface (GUI) for Bodgitt and Scarper, LLC.
suncertify.db Provides interfaces and classes for working with the DB interface and its Data implementation.
suncertify.protocol Provides interfaces and classes for working with Subcontractor objects and the SubcontractorCommand protocol.
suncertify.protocol.client Provides classes for developing local and remote (RMI) clients based on the SubcontractorCommand protocol.
suncertify.protocol.server Provides classes for developing RMI servers based on the SubcontractorCommand protocol.
